version_description: These instructions are for Zevon's posthumously released "Preludes" version of Accidentally Like a Martyr. It has a substantially different feel due to it's situation in a major Key. These instructions are in the key of F# . Despite this it is unclear what key the song is in as the piano, interestingly, may have been tuned a half step up or down one of the traditional keys.
